OL,3,CAlleged sword attacker tells court
OL,4,Cabout taking drugs and drinking own
OL,5,Curine
OL,7,FAn alleged sword attacker accused of
OL,8,Fvirtually decapitating a schoolboy in
OL,9,Fa drug-fuelled rampage in London has
OL,10,Ftold of taking psychedelics and
OL,11,Fdrinking his own urine years before
OL,12,Famid an interest in spirituality.
OL,14,FMarcus Arduini Monzo, 37, allegedly
OL,15,Fskinned and deboned his pet cat before
OL,16,Flaunching a 20-minute spree of
OL,17,Fviolence in Hainault, east London,
OL,18,Fwhile high on cannabis, the Old Bailey
OL,19,Fheard.
