OL,5,Curine
OL,7,FHe is accused of murdering 14-year-old
OL,8,FDaniel Anjorin, mowing down pedestrian
OL,9,FDonato Iwule with a van and attacking
OL,10,Ftwo police officers and a couple in
OL,11,Ftheir home on 30 April 2024.
OL,13,FGiving evidence on his background on
OL,14,FFriday, Monzo told the court he
OL,15,Fexperienced "bullying and violence"
OL,16,Fwhile growing up in Brazil.
OL,18,FHe moved to London in 2013, where he
OL,19,Fbegan smoking cannabis and took magic
OL,20,Fmushrooms a few times, jurors heard.
