OL,5,Curine
OL,7,FThe defendant said he stopped in 2015
OL,8,Fbecause cannabis made him feel
OL,9,F"unproductive" and "lazy", but resumed
OL,10,Fusing it years later.
OL,12,FFollowing a mixed martial arts (MMA)
OL,13,Finjury in 2016, Monzo turned to yoga
OL,14,Fand developed an increasing interest
OL,15,Fin spirituality, the court was told.
OL,17,FAsked what spirituality meant to him,
OL,18,Fhe said: "Exploring the subtle aspects
OL,19,Fof life ` the magical, miraculous and
OL,20,Fsupernatural."
