OL,4,Cabout taking drugs and drinking own
OL,5,Curine
OL,7,FAround 2017, he began following
OL,8,FYouTube spiritual guru Sadhguru, which
OL,9,Fled to a year-long stay in India,
OL,10,Fjurors heard.
OL,12,FMonzo said he was taught at a retreat
OL,13,Fto detach from family and friends.
OL,15,FDuring a weekend trip, he took
OL,16,Fayahuasca ` a hallucinogenic brew
OL,17,Ftraditionally used in South America.
