OL,5,Curine
OL,7,FHe returned to the UK "looking
OL,8,Fskinnier", before travelling to a
OL,9,Fremote part of Brazil to consume more
OL,10,Fayahuasca, the court heard.
OL,12,FMonzo also said he took ayahuasca
OL,13,Ftwice in the UK, describing it as
OL,14,Fhaving stronger effects during
OL,15,F"ceremonies".
OL,17,FHe later travelled again to Brazil and
OL,18,FIndia, and also attended breatharian
OL,19,Ffestivals in Italy and Denmark, which
OL,20,Fpromote living without food, jurors
OL,21,Fwere told.
