OL,5,Curine
OL,7,FOn his return to the UK, Monzo said he
OL,8,Fargued with family members because he
OL,9,Fwas "not very clean".
OL,11,FThe defendant told the court that he
OL,12,Fbegan drinking his own urine for
OL,13,F"cleaning" purposes.
OL,15,FHe added: "I would use it to shower,
OL,16,Fon the hair, even using it on the
OL,17,Fnose."
