OL,3,CAlleged sword attacker tells court
OL,4,Cabout taking drugs and drinking own
OL,5,Curine
OL,7,FMonzo allegedly used his Ford Transit
OL,8,Fto knock Mr Iwule into a garden, then
OL,9,Fslashed him in the neck with a samurai
OL,10,Fsword before the victim escaped,
OL,11,Fjurors were previously told.
OL,13,FHe then virtually decapitated Daniel,
OL,14,Fwho was wearing headphones on his way
OL,15,Fto school, the court heard.
OL,17,FPc Yasmin Mechem-Whitfield chased the
OL,18,Fdefendant through alleyways before he
OL,19,Fstruck her three times with the sword
OL,20,Fthat had a 60cm blade, prosecutors say.
