OL,7,FMonzo then allegedly entered a
OL,8,Fproperty and attacked a couple who
OL,9,Fwere sleeping in an upstairs bedroom
OL,10,Fwith their young daughter nearby.
OL,12,FHe also struck Inspector Moloy
OL,13,FCampbell once with the sword before he
OL,14,Fwas arrested.
OL,16,FAfterwards, he likened events to the
OL,17,FHollywood film The Hunger Games and
OL,18,Fclaimed to have an alternative
OL,19,Fpersonality of a "professional
OL,20,Fassassin".
