OL,3,CAlleged sword attacker tells court
OL,4,Cabout taking drugs and drinking own
OL,5,Curine
OL,7,FMonzo denies Daniel's murder and the
OL,8,Fattempted murders of Mr Iwule, Sindy
OL,9,FArias, Henry De Los Rios Polania and
OL,10,FMs Mechem-Whitfield, as well as
OL,11,Fwounding Mr Campbell with intent.
OL,13,FHe also denies aggravated burglary and
OL,14,Fpossession of a bladed article
OL,15,Frelating to a kitchen knife.
OL,17,FMonzo has admitted having two swords.
OL,19,FThe trial continues.
